Calculated enrichment and visual plot¶

In [3]:
save_ggplots <- function(fn, p, w, h){
    for(ext in c('.pdf', '.png', '.svg')){
        ggsave(paste0(fn, ext), plot=p, width=w, height=h)
    }
}
